	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid hi ferant, ex ipsis cognosces.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevenses</placeName> multum sibi sumpserunt in thesibus istis explicandis et ordinandis; sed simul quoque temporis sibi multum sumpserunt; nam integro mense isti substiterunt illic.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miramur hanc gentem tot calamitatibus non posse adigi ad concordiam et de rebus tam leviculis tantum schisma oriri; miramur hos tantulum negotium tot ambagibus et thesibus nunquam finiendis explicare.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Subscripserant nostri <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l280" cert="high">Lausanenses</placeName> <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevensium</placeName> expositioni; sed quoniam illud erat periculosum et non sine offensa magistratus, siquidem scire potuisset, factum fuisset, effecimus commoda ratione, ut Lausanensium scriptum rursum ab his extorqueremus, et dedimus illis commune scriptum ecclesiae <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernensis</placeName> nomine, sub qua etiam <placeName ref="l280" cert="high">Lausanensis</placeName> comprehenditur, quod quale sit, videbis.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puto neminem propter hoc nos reprehendere posse, et putamus vos quoque eadem cautione usuros.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alias quod nunc scribam, non habeo.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pax in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> mediocriter procedit.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Minitatur rex vim et iam papistis suis, qui eam servare nolint.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea nec <persName type="auto_name">Condaeus</persName> nec amiralius adhuc sunt in aula.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l167" cert="high">Genevę</placeName> pestis magis ac magis invalescit; hinc fit, ut plęrique discedant.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expectamus hodie hic filium principis Palatini <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8024">Christophorum</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8063" cert="high">Steigerus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7449" cert="high">Diesbachius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7511" cert="high">Gravenrietus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" cert="low" ref="p21017">Manuel</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4060">Zehenderi</persName> et socer te plurimum salutant; idem facit <persName type="auto_name">Blasius</persName>, meus gener, qui hic adest et per quem ab his legatis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l280" cert="high">Lausanensium</placeName> subscriptionem commode rursus extorsimus.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Precor benedictionem et salutem tuis omnibus.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te item fratres et symmystae.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 13. iulii 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[ohannes] Hallerus</persName>, perpetuo tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, pastori ecclesiae <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> fidelissimo, domino meo honorando et compatri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
